Package: MonotoneEI
Type: Package
Title: Implement Monotone Ecological Inference from Elzayn et al., 2025
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Claire", "Morton", email = "mortonc@stanford.edu",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package implements the Method of Bounds, Ecological Regression, 
    and the Neighborhood Model to assist with ecological inference. It includes
    functions to plot these bounds/point estimates and create bootstrap 
    confidence intervals.
